page.title: 11Houses
page.content: The houses are mostly farm cottages built out of stone but few more modern houses are built out of brick with harled walls.Nearly evey single one is roofed with red pan tiles but the occasional house has grey slates.Almost all the farm cottages are built in rows but most of the modern houses ar detached vilas.The farm cottages are single storey but the farm houses,private houses and council houses have two storeys.Farm cottages mostly have a kitchen, a living room,a bathroom and two or three bedrooms while the private houses,farm houses, and council houses have a living room,a bathroom,a few bedrooms, a dining room and a utility room.The modern houses have gardens right round them while most of the farm cottages have their gardens at the back of the house.
